stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE: reset

    IDLE --> ACTIVATING: ACT cmd

    ACTIVATING --> ACTIVE: tRCD elapsed

    ACTIVE --> RD_BUSY: RD cmd
    ACTIVE --> WR_BUSY: WR cmd
    ACTIVE --> PRECHARGING: PRE cmd (tRAS met)

    RD_BUSY --> ACTIVE: CL+BL beats done
    RD_BUSY --> PRECHARGING: RDA (auto-pre)

    WR_BUSY --> ACTIVE: CWL+BL beats done
    WR_BUSY --> PRECHARGING: WRA (auto-pre)

    PRECHARGING --> IDLE: tRP elapsed

    IDLE --> REFRESHING: REFpb cmd (LPDDR2)
    REFRESHING --> IDLE: tRFCpb elapsed

    note right of ACTIVATING
      Counts tRCD
      open_row stored
    end note

    note right of WR_BUSY
      Counts CWL pipeline
      then BL beats
      then tWR
    end note

    note left of PRECHARGING
      Triggered by:
      - explicit PRE
      - RDA / WRA
      - row conflict
    end note
